                         the Binomial Spatial model
covariog                 Empirical Covariogram for a Model with log-link
                         and an Underlying Gaussian Field
covariog.model.env       Envelope for Empirical Covariogram for the
                         Poisson-log normal model
lines.covariomodel       Line with a Covariogram Model
mcmc.control             Defines options for the MCMC-algorithm
model.glm.control        Defines model options
output.glm.control       Defines output options
plot.covariogram         Plot Empirical Covariogram
pois.krige.bayes         Bayesian Posterior Simulation and Prediction for
                         the Poisson Spatial model
pois.likfit.sim          Monte Carlo Maximum Likelihood Estimation for
                         the Poisson normal model
pois.log.krige           Conditional Simulation and Prediction for the
                         Poisson-log Spatial model
prepare.lik.sim          Prepare for Monte Carlo MLE
prior.glm.control        Defines prior options
rongelap                 Radionuclide Concentrations on Rongelap Island
